<topic id="d0e333" xml:lang="en-US">
  <title>const detect</title>

  <body>
    <p>Format:</p>

    <codeblock>          -[no-]const-detect</codeblock>

    <p>enable/disable constant detection</p>

    <p>Default: disabled</p>

    <p>Purpose: Look for variables that are only assigned a single, constant
    value and replace them with that constant value.</p>
  </body>
